  "title": "Legal Assistant [Central | MNC]",
  "description": "<p><strong>[Job ID: 1424971]</strong></p><p><strong>Responsibilities:</strong></p><p><strong>Legal Support Activities</strong></p><ul><li>Conduct basic legal and factual research under guidance, including online searches and retrieval of publicly available information.</li><li>Support corporate secretarial activities, including liaison with the appointed corporate secretarial service provider.</li><li>Assist with submission and review of internal applications by collecting documents, checking completeness, and confirming factual information with relevant stakeholders.</li></ul><p><strong>Administrative and Operational Support</strong></p><ul><li>Maintain documentation and filing systems, including electronic and physical records, shared folders, and scanned PDFs.</li><li>Circulate and file internal applications as required.</li><li>Coordinate business travel arrangements for Legal team members, including flight and hotel bookings, itineraries, and related logistics.</li><li>Support billing, accounting, invoicing, and claims reimbursement processes.</li><li>Assist with procurement, management, and disposal of office stationery, books, and subscriptions.</li><li>Provide general administrative and clerical support to the Legal Department.</li></ul><p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p><ul><li><strong>Minimum 1 year of experience in administrative support, legal assistance, secretarial, paralegal, or corporate support roles; in‑house or law firm experience is an added advantage.</strong></li><li>Ability to work effectively both independently and in a team environment.</li><li>High level of thoroughness and attention to detail.</li></ul><p>We regret that only shortlisted candidates will be notified. However, rest assured that all applications will be updated to our resume bank for future opportunities.</p><p>Please kindly refer to the Privacy Policy of Good Job Creations for your reference: https://goodjobcreations.com.sg/en/privacy-policy/</p><p>EA Personnel Name: Felicia Chiam Kar Min<br />EA Personnel Reg. No.: R25152370<br />EA Licence No.: 07C5771 </p>",
